name: Alpha Venture DAO
intro: One-stop site for builders to start Web3 projects
introduce: Alpha Venture DAO is a one-stop station for builders to kickstart their Web3 projects. Alpha Incubate selects and mentors high quality Web3 projects to ensure the projects launch successfully with strong product-market fit, community, investors, and growth trajectory. Incubated projects can tap Alpha Network, more than 50 global firms, thought leaders and top-minds in Web3, for support and mentorship throughout the program. Alpha aims to create a community of builders that focuses on long-term innovation who come together to push the boundary of Web3 by creating innovative use cases.
